## 12. Legal Compliance

This Privacy Policy complies with:
- **General Data Protection Law (LGPD)** - Law No. 13,709/2018 (Brazil)
- **Internet Civil Rights Framework** - Law No. 12,965/2014 (Brazil)
- **Consumer Protection Code** - Law No. 8,078/1990 (Brazil)

